column5: Not only very tallented but I really enjoyed the song as well as the way it is done.  https://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&v=Syz5CAXCQ68
Yes, I like that one too, Cliff. They don't need a ton of and thousands of $$ worth of electronic voice and sound embellishment gear either.

Just the words have so much meaning too! It is just one of those songs that has a wonderful meaning and the way it is presented fits the words perfectly right down to the smiles as they are singing it. I think I've listened to it about 10 times already!
I'll  bet that took some serious practice, nicely done.
Saw that a couple of days ago, very cool indeed, and very enjoyable  maureen
